{"type":"message","id":"13e4131a","parentId":"7e8fb568","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:37:12.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the most recent pulse log. Let me read it.","thinkingSignature":"86e56e6acde9e92f78f56d1f321d07ae63d0e75477da5a2acfebc8f143869bc2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v7sno58cqol5_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\pulse_2026-03-24 083626.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1089,"output":66,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13292,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774355830004}}
{"type":"message","id":"87958244","parentId":"13e4131a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:37:12.514Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_v7sno58cqol5_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# Pulse: 2026-03-24 083626\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: scripts/tic-classifier.ps1 (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLooking at the goals and context:\r\n\r\n1. Phase 0 and Phase 1 are complete\r\n2. Key pending task: **TIC Experiment** (Temporal Invariance Compression)\r\n   - Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n   - Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n   - Predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n\r\nThe insight is that compression and causal discovery are the same problem. The next action is to implement the TIC classifier.\r\n\r\nLet me think about what this would look like:\r\n\r\n1. Read recent pulse logs from `logs/` directory\r\n2. Build a simple classifier that identifies:\r\n   - Invariant structures (stable patterns across pulses)\r\n   - Variant structures (changing content)\r\n3. Test prediction of next pulse based on invariants\r\n\r\nFor this pulse, I should create a concrete implementation artifact. Let me create a TIC experiment script or document that advances this.\r\n\r\nI'll create a `tic_experiment.ps1` or similar script that:\r\n- Reads pulse logs\r\n- Identifies invariant patterns (file headers, structure)\r\n- Identifies variant content\r\n- Tests classification accuracy\r\n- Tests next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nLet me write a PowerShell script that implements the TIC classifier.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the critical next step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariant vs variant structures across pulse logs.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate `tic/tic_classifier.ps1` - a PowerShell script that:\r\n- Reads pulse logs from `logs/` directory\r\n- Extracts structural invariants (timestamps, file headers, section markers)\r\n- Identifies variant content (ideas, findings, pending items)\r\n- Tests invariant/variant classification on held-out data\r\n- Validates next-pulse prediction from invariant structures\r\n\r\nThis directly advances the Phase 1 advancement by implementing the TIC experiment.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Experiment\r\n# Tests hypothesis: causal structure = invariant structure\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$MinPulseCount = 5,\r\n    [int]$TrainSplit = 0.7,\r\n    [string]$LogsPath = \"logs\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n\r\n# --- Invariant Patterns (structural) ---\r\n$INVARIANT_PATTERNS = @(\r\n    '^\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}',           # Date stamps\r\n    '^### ',                          # Section headers\r\n    '^## ',                           # Major headers\r\n    '^\\[ \\] ',                        # Checkbox items\r\n    '^\\[x\\] ',                        # Checked items\r\n    '^-\\s+\\[',                        # Linked items\r\n    '^\\w+:\\s*$',                      # Key: format\r\n    '^```'                            # Code blocks\r\n)\r\n\r\n# --- Variant Patterns (content) ---\r\n$VARIANT_INDICATORS = @(\r\n    '^\\s*-\\s+[A-Z]',                  # Bullet points with caps (ideas)\r\n    '^\\s*\\*\\s+[A-Z]',\r\n    '^\\s*>\\s+',                       # Blockquotes (insights)\r\n    '\\b(hypothesis|insight|theory)\\b',\r\n    '\\b(complete|pending|active)\\b'\r\n)\r\n\r\nfunction Get-PulseLog {\r\n    param([string]$Path)\r\n    \r\n    $files = Get-ChildItem -Path $Path -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | \r\n             Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending\r\n    \r\n    if ($files.Count -lt $MinPulseCount) {\r\n        Write-Warning \"Need at least $MinPulseCount pulses, found $($files.Count)\"\r\n        return @()\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $files\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Test-IsInvariant {\r\n    param([string]$Line)\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($pattern in $INVARIANT_PATTERNS) {\r\n        if ($Line -match $pattern) { return $true }\r\n    }\r\n    return $false\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Test-IsVariant {\r\n    param([string]$Line)\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($pattern in $VARIANT_INDICATORS) {\r\n        if ($Line -match $pattern) { return $true }\r\n    }\r\n    return $false\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Get-TICClassification {\r\n    param([string[]]$Lines)\r\n    \r\n    $result = @{\r\n        InvariantLines = @()\r\n        VariantLines = @()\r\n        UnclassifiedLines = @()\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($line in $Lines) {\r\n        if ($line -match '^\\s*$') { continue }  # Skip empty\r\n        \r\n        if (Test-IsInvariant -Line $line) {\r\n            $result.InvariantLines += $line\r\n        } elseif (Test-IsVariant -Line $line) {\r\n            $result.VariantLines += $line\r\n        } else {\r\n            $result.UnclassifiedLines += $line\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $result\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Invoke-TICExperiment {\r\n    Write-Host \"=== TIC Experiment ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\n    \r\n    $pulses = Get-PulseLog -Path $LogsPath\r\n    if ($pulses.Count -eq 0) { return }\r\n    \r\n    Write-Host \"Found $($pulses.Count) pulse logs\"\r\n    \r\n    # Split into train/test\r\n    $splitIdx = [math]::Floor($pulses.Count * $TrainSplit)\r\n    $trainPulses = $pulses[0..($splitIdx-1)]\r\n    $testPulses = $pulses[$splitIdx..($pulses.Count-1)]\r\n    \r\n    Write-Host \"Train: $($trainPulses.Count), Test: $($testPulses.Count)\"\r\n    \r\n    # Build invariant vocabulary from training set\r\n    $invariantSet = @{}\r\n    $variantSet = @{}\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($pulse in $trainPulses) {\r\n        $content = Get-\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 08:36:56\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774355832512}}
