for the next pulse to pick up.\n\n**Context:** This advances the Phase 1 \"Compression-Causal Duality\" insight: Problems 1 (compression) and 2 (causal discovery) are the same problem. Phase 1 and Phase 2 collapse into one."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5167,"output":446,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17750,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774355867082}}
